18 "§ 163-362. Counting of ballots.
19 Counting of ballots in primaries and elections held under this Article shall be under the same
20 rules as for counting of ballots in nonpartisan municipal elections under Article 24 of this
21 Chapter.
22 "§ 163-363. Other rules.
23 Except as provided by this Article, the conduct of elections shall be governed by Subchapter
24 VI of this Chapter."
25 SECTION 2.2. This Part becomes effective with respect to primaries and elections
