17 "(d) Registration Deadlines for a Primary or Election. – In order to be valid for a primary
18 or election, the form:form must comply with one of the following:
19 (1) If submitted by mail, must be postmarked at least 25 days before the primary
20 or election, except that any mailed application on which the postmark is
